706728f-a.title: Brooklyn: Sheepshead Bay Road - Neptune Avenue
706728f-a.text:
Sheepshead Bay Road, north side, east from its intersection with Nep-
tune Ave., to West 6th Street. The cupola, near the smokestack, polnts out
the Coney Island House.
October 1928.
Eugene L. Armbruster Collection.
MAY BE REPRODUCED.
